  "text": "For Asperaxis karenae [CITATION_1] , mtMutS data was already available in GenBank (accession number DQ302847.1) [CITATION_2] . To investigate the position of this subfamily compared to our Melithaeinae specimens, we have included the sequence in our mtMutS dataset. As outgroup we have used the same specimens as in the previous analyses.",
